{"type": "article", "id": 46206, "title": "看这包装，吃蟋蟀蛋白棒或许没那么吓人了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-10-17T22:52:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 12947, "name": "EXO"}, {"id": 44766, "name": "Gander"}, {"id": 44767, "name": "OXO"}, {"id": 44768, "name": "Astro HQ"}, {"id": 44769, "name": "Smart Design"}, {"id": 27825, "name": "Fernando Mastrangelo"}, {"id": 39342, "name": "Jiyoun Kim"}, {"id": 44770, "name": "Asya Kozina"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 93, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171017172154aT81x2QZwioSsDGc.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>EXO by Gander</h3><p>在如何帮助潜在顾客克服把昆虫吃进嘴里这件事上，创意机构为可食用昆虫制品品牌策划了风趣的亲民路线，我们之前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/42502.html\">蟋蟀薯片包装</a>就是一个典型的案例。今天介绍的美国蟋蟀蛋白棒品牌 EXO 由设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.takeagander.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gander</a> 操刀视觉形象，黑白色的原料照片、人们运动的场景以及手绘涂鸦巧妙地组合在一起，包装上能够联系到其风味的彩色部分则起到了中和的作用，营造出一种轻松明快的气质。如果你想试试这些蛋白棒，可以通过<a href=\"https://exoprotein.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买，一套 12 根的售价为 36 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172221f9QbyC8ncV3kxWEK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.536000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172220vRBboeqDJg21Glrx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.533000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172221qzguE76ITHc4C0lt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172221cPTsu3C1k9ewmJqG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172221x6Njh7eb5sBu39yG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Luna Display by Astro HQ</h3><p>2015 年，两位前苹果工程师创立了一个名为 Astro HQ 的设计公司，负责优化苹果产品使用体验和研发相关配件。最近，他们发布了一款名为 Luna 的产品，它能够让 iPad 成为第二个电脑屏幕。大小相当于 U 盘的 Luna 携带起来非常方便，在外出办公但无法携带双屏幕的情况下，让用户可以直接用 iPad 进行更方便的操作。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/767721702/luna-display\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 65 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172243LKlGQsE3BdkYDCnq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558824\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172243j5gtcBZVoY9imD0z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172243WwJkPViR9BcfD0gN.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558824\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Quick-Release Apple Corer by Smart Design</h3><p>想做苹果有关的料理，但为取核头疼？来自设计公司 <a href=\"https://smartdesignworldwide.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Smart Design</a> 的 <a href=\"http://francoisdmd.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">François de Martrin-Donos</a> 为美国品牌 <a href=\"https://www.oxo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OXO</a> 开发的取核工具可以让人省心不少。它就像是一把优化过的夹子，只要用它贯穿苹果正中央，夹住核之后取出即可。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.oxo.com/products/preparing/fruit-vegetable-tools/quick-release-apple-corer\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买，售价为 11.99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710171722571hwdmZoX8WVGnHzp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172258GhpfnYo2wJRuTld1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172258UW2jvcVLbPzTRu5a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Reverence by Fernando Mastrangelo</h3><p>崩裂的冰盖、枯竭的水域、国家公园内的山脉……来自布鲁克林的艺术家 <a href=\"https://www.fernandomastrangelo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fernando Mastrangelo</a> 通过这套为纽约高档地毯品牌 <a href=\"http://www.edwardfields.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Edward Fields</a> 设计的 Reverence 系列，表达了自己对大自然的敬畏之情。这些色调柔和、忠于现实的地毯就像是利用水彩绘制的俯瞰图，Mastrangelo 还特意以 Melt and Crash、Break 这类名词为它们命名，敲响气候变化的警钟。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172308tLQcUObBV014Kg5z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694836\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710171723088eabwj2O1YtdNpxg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172309NO2wMF8SQUg53hoV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172308406ubonBEvSi5gKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lightning lamp by Jiyoun Kim</h3><p>在上月举行的伦敦设计节上，韩国产品设计师 <a href=\"http://www.jiyounkim.com/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jiyoun Kim</a> 带来了一套颇有漫画感的闪电灯。他的灵感来源于一句古老的韩国谚语，它的含义类似中文里的“晴天霹雳”，同时还暗喻人生无常，人们需要时不时调整自己对生活的展望。闪电和底座部分以不锈钢为原材料，顶部的云灯罩则是玻璃吹制而成。几种不同的配色则是 Kim 根据清晨、正午、黄昏和午夜所设计的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172322E83bAq6XzhRfOLIl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737164\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172322Mq5CdLpa8xbjFuyB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.764059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172320DQg3wREfCrMsS4JW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687042\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710171723205Swa9sDErtYkpWhe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.996333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172323ie1pTxO4rzyFCNUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657702\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Paper wigs by Asya Kozina</h3><p>来自俄罗斯的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/asyakozina\" rel=\"nofollow\">Asya Kozina</a> 是一名精通纸艺的艺术家，并凭借着用纸还原的一系列<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/21079875/Mongolian-costumes\" rel=\"nofollow\">蒙古传统服饰</a>为人所知。继“纸衣”之后，喜欢用纸来诠释不同文化和历史时期的 Kozina 最近又以巴洛克时期那些华丽的假发为灵感，用纸进行了一番再创作：在这些夸张的巨型假发上，你甚至可以发现摩天大楼、飞机、帆船。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172423PyEIscnLKpx60uMZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172424ESQ3DBuzJYto57VW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497555\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172423aNyRHeXWj90pJvu3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497555\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171017172425aN958mcCX6TKU0Ih.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497555\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}